{"word":"H7969 - שָׁלֹושׁ - shâlôwsh - shaw-loshe' - Fork","slug":"H7969","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁלֹושׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâlôwsh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-loshe'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fork"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05D5;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05D5;&#x05E9;&#x05C1; - sha&#x0302;lo&#x0302;sh  sha&#x0302;lo&#x0302;sh  sh<sup>e</sup>lo&#x0302;sha&#x0302;h  sh<sup>e</sup>lo&#x0302;sha&#x0302;h</b> - <i>(1,2) shaw-loshe', (3,4) shel-o-shaw'</i><p/>The last two forms being masculine; a primitive number; <i>three</i>; occasionally (ordinal) <i>third</i>, or (multiplicative) <i>thrice</i>: -  + fork, + often [-times], third, thir [-teen, -teenth], three, + thrice. Compare <a href=\"#/H7991\">H7991</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7597\">H7597</a>, <a href=\"#/H7970\">H7970</a>, <a href=\"#/H7991\">H7991</a>, <a href=\"#/H7992\">H7992</a>, <a href=\"#/H8027\">H8027</a>, <a href=\"#/H8028\">H8028</a>, <a href=\"#/H8029\">H8029</a>, <a href=\"#/H8030\">H8030</a>, <a href=\"#/H8031\">H8031</a>, <a href=\"#/H8032\">H8032</a>"}]}